### Templates API Test Suite
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/templates
### Auth: Bearer token required (Clerk JWT)

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = your_clerk_jwt_token_here
@templateId = replace_with_actual_template_id

### 1. Create template
POST {{baseUrl}}/templates
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "content",
  "label": "Product Launch Template",
  "description": "Template for announcing new product releases",
  "content": "Introducing {{product_name}}! 🚀\n\n{{benefits}}\n\n{{cta}}",
  "category": "caption",
  "variables": ["product_name", "benefits", "cta"],
  "categories": ["marketing", "announcements"],
  "industries": ["technology", "saas"],
  "platforms": ["instagram", "twitter", "linkedin"]
}

### 2. List templates (with filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/templates?category=caption&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get template by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/templates/{{templateId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Update template
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/templates/{{templateId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "content",
  "label": "Product Launch Template v2",
  "description": "Updated template with better CTAs"
}

### 5. Delete template
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/templates/{{templateId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Use template (fill variables)
POST {{baseUrl}}/templates/{{templateId}}/use
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variables": {
    "product_name": "Amazing Widget Pro",
    "benefits": "Save 10 hours per week with automation",
    "cta": "Order now and get 20% off! Link in bio 👆"
  }
}

### 7. Get AI template suggestions
POST {{baseUrl}}/templates/suggest
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "goal": "increase engagement",
  "category": "caption",
  "platform": "instagram",
  "industry": "technology"
}

### 8. Get popular templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/templates/popular?limit=5&category=caption
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


